---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="toki-flow">
    <div class="intro">
      <h1>TOKI FLOW</h1>
      <p>
        TOKI Flow <strong>transforms insights into solutions</strong> that create value for brand, customer, and planet. Our <strong>five paths</strong> guide a journey from understanding to changeâ€”each can stand alone, or we can navigate them together
        as a partnership. We don't just deliver a task; we create movement, clarity, and tangible results.
      </p>

      <img src="public/toki_flow.png" alt="logo" class="intro-img" />
    </div>

    <div class="fase1">
      <div class="tekst1">
        <h2>FASE 1</h2>
        <h3>Understanding Your Reality</h3>
        <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Map your packaging journey to uncover value for business, brand, and sustainability.</p>
        <p><strong>How:</strong> Analyze current setup, identify opportunities, and align on next steps.</p>
        <p><strong>Investment:</strong> 25,000 - 30,000 DKK.</p>
      </div>

      <img src="public/fase1.png" alt="fase1" class="fase-icon" />
    </div>

    <div class="fase2">
      <div class="tekst2">
        <h2>FASE 2</h2>
        <h3>Shape Your Design DNA</h3>
        <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Define visual and structural principles for cohesive, brand-aligned packaging.</p>
        <p><strong>How:</strong> Workshop to create design guidelines and a "Packaging DNA Compass."</p>
        <p><strong>Investment:</strong> 25,000 - 30,000 DKK.</p>
      </div>

      <img src="public/fase2.png" alt="fase2" class="fase-icon" />
    </div>

    <div class="fase3">
      <div class="tekst3">
        <h2>FASE 3</h2>
        <h3>Make Ideas Tangible</h3>
        <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Turn principles into testable concepts-visual, functional, and commercial.</p>
        <p><strong>How:</strong> Develop 2 - 3 prototypes, visualize in context, and select the best direction.</p>
        <p><strong>Investment:</strong> 35,000 - 40,000 DKK.</p>
      </div>
      <img src="public/fase3.png" alt="fase3" class="fase-icon" />
    </div>

    <div class="fase4">
      <div class="tekst4">
        <h2>FASE 4</h2>
        <h3>Prepare for the World</h3>
        <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Refine the chosen concept for production-ready to perform in real life.</p>
        <p><strong>How:</strong> Prototype, test, adjust, and align design, tech, and supply chain.</p>
        <p><strong>Investment:</strong> 40,000 - 45,000 DKK.</p>
      </div>
      <img src="public/fase4.png" alt="fase4" class="fase-icon" />
    </div>

    <div class="fase5">
      <div class="tekst5">
        <h2>FASE 5</h2>
        <h3>Scale Together</h3>
        <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Build a scalable system with the right partners for global, sustainable impact.</p>
        <p><strong>How:</strong> Match suppliers, set up collaboration, and optimize continuously.</p>
        <p><strong>Investment:</strong> From 18,000 DKK (advisory) to 60,000+ DKK (full scaling).</p>
      </div>

      <img src="public/fase5.png" alt="fase5" class="fase-icon" />
    </div>

    <p><class="footer-text">From insight to impact, we balance strategy, storytelling, and sustainability to deliver packaging that truly matters.</class="footer-text"></p>
    <Layout />

    <style>
      .toki-flow {
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 40px 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #bac8d9;
      }

      .intro {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
        gap: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 60px;
      }

      .intro-img {
        width: 70%;
        height: auto;
        grid-column: 3;
      }
      /* 
  .tekst1 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 2fr;
  } */

      .fase {
        border-top: 3px solid #0d0c0c;
        padding: 40px 0;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 2fr;
        /* gap: 20px; */
      }

      .fase2,
      .fase4 {
        border-bottom: 3px solid #0d0c0c;
        padding: 40px 0;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 2fr;
        /* gap: 20px; */
      }
      .tekst2,
      .tekst4 {
        display: grid;
        grid-column: auto;
      }
      .tekst1,
      .tekst3,
      .tekst5 {
        display: grid;
        grid-auto-columns: auto;
      }

      .fase-icon {
        width: 100px;
        height: auto;
        justify-self: end;
      }

      .fase h2 {
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }

      .fase h3 {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-decoration: underline;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
    </style>
  </section></Layout
>
